### Create PaymentIntent - Valid request
POST http://localhost:3000/api/checkout/create-intent
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "femaleQty": 2,
  "maleQty": 1,
  "language": "en"
}


###----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

### Create PaymentIntent - Both zero (should fail)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/checkout/create-intent
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "femaleQty": 0,
  "maleQty": 0,
  "language": "en"
}
###----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------



### Create PaymentIntent - Negative (should fail)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/checkout/create-intent
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "femaleQty": -1,
  "maleQty": 1,
  "language": "en"
}
