################################
### Tickets Testing (requires valid auth token from above) - Correct PIN
################################

###----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


### Fetch all valid tickets-not scanned yet (replace YOUR_TOKEN with the token from auth) =>> requires Test Scanner Auth — Correct PIN First
