Authorization: Bearer cda0c170cb48bde3dfd2e08f6a62aab859590659f6dcd8976b14c5fccbf86b6c
##Authorization: Bearer EXAMPLE_aaaa55fdae5b25....


###----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

### Scan a ticket (replace QR_TOKEN with a real qr_token from the tickets response)
